content: <?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?> <rdf:RDF   xmlns:dcterms="http://purl.org/dc/terms/"   xmlns:documentcontainer="http://eidchub.ceh.ac.uk/portal_types/documentContainer#"   xmlns:file="http://eidchub.ceh.ac.uk/portal_types/File#"   xmlns:rdf="http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#" >   <documentcontainer:documentContainer rdf:about="http://eidchub.ceh.ac.uk/metadata/cd7db09f-edf6-4b06-b878-f1be6c649e3a">     <dcterms:modified rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2014-09-30T10:57:46Z</dcterms:modified>     <documentcontainer:fileIdentifier xml:lang="en">cd7db09f-edf6-4b06-b878-f1be6c649e3a</documentcontainer:fileIdentifier>     <dcterms:created rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2012-01-03T14:00:35Z</dcterms:created>     <dcterms:hasPart>       <file:File rdf:about="http://eidchub.ceh.ac.uk/metadata/cd7db09f-edf6-4b06-b878-f1be6c649e3a/detailed-metadata">         <dcterms:modified rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2012-01-03T14:01:55Z</dcterms:modified>         <dcterms:created rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2012-01-03T14:01:55Z</dcterms:created>         <dcterms:isPartOf rdf:resource="http://eidchub.ceh.ac.uk/metadata/cd7db09f-edf6-4b06-b878-f1be6c649e3a"/>         <dcterms:creator>dgwr</dcterms:creator>         <file:id xml:lang="en">detailed-metadata</file:id>         <dcterms:title xml:lang="en">Detailed metadata </dcterms:title>       </file:File>     </dcterms:hasPart>     <dcterms:issued rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2012-01-03T14:25:00Z</dcterms:issued>     <dcterms:isPartOf rdf:resource="http://eidchub.ceh.ac.uk/metadata"/>     <dcterms:creator>dgwr</dcterms:creator>     <dcterms:description xml:lang="en">Discharge data and in-stream temperature for a peatland headwater stream of the Conwy catchment, North Wales are presented from march 2008 until present. The stream for which the data represents is the Nant y Brwyn situated on the Migneint blanket bog within Snowdonia National Park. The purpose of the data is to calculate annual run-off estimates for the Nant y Brwyn catchment and to provide support for estimating fluvial carbon fluxes. Note: there are gaps in this data set due to equipment/battery failures and/or freezing of the stream.</dcterms:description>     <documentcontainer:id xml:lang="en">cd7db09f-edf6-4b06-b878-f1be6c649e3a</documentcontainer:id>     <dcterms:subject>Wales</dcterms:subject>     <dcterms:subject>CEH Biogeochemistry Programme</dcterms:subject>     <dcterms:subject>CEH Project NEC04016 T3</dcterms:subject>     <dcterms:subject>UK</dcterms:subject>     <dcterms:subject>continuous</dcterms:subject>     <dcterms:subject>NERC_DDC</dcterms:subject>     <dcterms:subject>Conwy Catchment</dcterms:subject>     <dcterms:subject>stream</dcterms:subject>     <dcterms:subject>Hydrometry</dcterms:subject>     <dcterms:subject>Environmental monitoring facilities</dcterms:subject>     <dcterms:subject>Water Resources</dcterms:subject>     <dcterms:title xml:lang="en">Conwy Catchment - Nant Y Brwyn Discharge dataset</dcterms:title>     <documentcontainer:catalogLink>http://data.ceh.ac.uk/metadata/cd7db09f-edf6-4b06-b878-f1be6c649e3a</documentcontainer:catalogLink>   </documentcontainer:documentContainer> </rdf:RDF>
